{"root":{"data":{"id":"djvo6m47cn40","created":1783765743933,"text":"阴司","font-size":48,"font-weight":"bold"},"children":[{"data":{"id":"djvo7wqdtzs0","created":1783765845406,"text":"地藏王","font-size":24,"font-weight":"bold","layout":null},"children":[{"data":{"id":"djvo81o1oa80","created":1783765856149,"text":"1秦广王:专司人间寿夭生死，统管吉凶。善人直接接引，恶人交予其他各殿审判","priority":null,"font-size":16,"layout":null},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"djvo8ofcwbs0","created":1783765905689,"text":"2楚江王:掌管活大地狱（寒冰地狱），惩罚在阳间伤人肢体、奸盗杀生等罪","priority":null,"font-size":16,"layout":null},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"djvo8wymbcg0","created":1783765924268,"text":"3宋帝王:掌管黑绳大地狱，惩罚阳间忤逆尊长、背信弃义、教唆兴讼等罪","priority":null,"font-size":16,"layout":null},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"djvo9ml3frs0","created":1783765980048,"text":"4五官王:掌管合大地狱（血池地狱），惩罚阳间逃税、欺诈、耍赖欠租等罪","priority":null,"font-size":16,"layout":null},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"djvoaatx5k80","created":1783766032823,"text":"5阎罗王:掌管叫唤大地狱。传说他本居第一殿，因怜悯屈死者而屡放还阳，被降调至此","font-size":16,"layout":null},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"djvoaicnji00","created":1783766049194,"text":"6卞城王:掌管大叫唤大地狱及枉死城，惩罚阳间怨天尤人、不敬神佛等罪","layout":null},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"djvocdpzsl40","created":1783766195845,"text":"7泰山王:掌管热恼大地狱，惩罚阳间取尸骨制药、离间他人至亲等罪","layout":null},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"djvocojmzzk0","created":1783766219405,"text":"8都市王:掌管大热恼大地狱，惩罚阳间不孝父母翁姑等罪","layout":null},"children":[]}]}]},"template":"default","theme":"wire","version":"1.4.43"}